[Although it is stated that all the culture-positive cases are members of the high school football team, it is not clear how many of the ill but not cultured -- or not culture positive -- are also members of the team.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2817542,41656. A map of the counties in the state of Wisconsin showing Pepin county in the western part of the state can be found at http://geology.com/county-map/wisconsin-county-map.gif. - Mod.LL]
